{
  "_comment": "Local URI->schema/SHACL map for ConformanceValidate.py --source local. Each CDIF profile maps to its framed JSON Schema (where one exists in this repo: discovery, data_description, complete) and its per-profile SHACL shapes (scoped to that profile, no cross-profile requirements). A record is validated against exactly the profiles its catalog record declares, so a discovery+provenance+manifest record is checked against provenance/manifest shapes without being required to carry data-description content. Both 1.0 and 1.1 versions map to the same artifacts. Paths are relative to this file; trailing-slash and datadescription/data_description insensitive.",

